== Dependecies ==
 - GPG
 - GPGME
 - C++-compiler (I used g++) and GPGME-devel-packages for compiling

== Compile & Install ==

How to compile & install:
	$ cd schluesselwaerter
	$ g++ schluesselwaerter.cpp -lgpgme -o schluesselwaerter
	$ cp schluesselwaerter /usr/bin
   How to install language-support:
	$ cp translations/schluesselwaerter-<wished language>.mo /usr/share/locale/<wished language>/LC_MESSAGES/
How to compile for 'portable' use with language support:
	$ cd schluesselwaerter
	$ sed --in-place schluesselwaerter.cpp --expression='s!textpath="/usr/share/locale"!textpath="locale"!'
	$ g++ schluesselwaerter.cpp -lgpgme -o schluesselwaerter
	$ mkdir locale/<wished language>/LC_MESSAGES
	$ cp translations/schluesselwaerter-<wished language>.mo locale/<wished language>/LC_MESSAGES/
How to translate and install:
	$ cd schluesselwaerter
	$ ./translate -i <lang_LANG>
	$ g++ schluesselwaerter.cpp -lgpgme -o schluesselwaerter
	$ ./translate -f -i <lang_LANG>
	$ cp schluesselwaerter /usr/bin
	$ cp translations/schluesselwaerter-<lang_LANG>.mo /usr/share/locale/<lang_LANG>/LC_MESSAGES/
How to translate for 'portable' use:
	comming next

